critical_positive: Due to COVID-19 and a lot of the effects that the pandemic has caused, I feel that conversations around these topics worked well. We were able to talk about how the pandemic has affected us, our well-beings, and our loved ones. In addition, we were able to talk about the impact on travel and our jobs due to COVID-19.

rest_of_day_open: I am hopeful for the rest of the week. I believe it will be successful. I having been working on my physical fitness and diet. Both have been going well. critical_positive: Well most of our conversation centered around COVID. Having a global pandemic which most people have never seen is definitely a subject matter that people have thoughts, opinions, and stories on. Additionally it has impacted basically everyone's life so people have a personal experience to share in regards to the current global situation.
